content: I applaud the minimalism but it's so difficult to upgrade without sending a request. In fact, they stopped responding to my emails last week. If WeWork can't even fix a simple little bug, I have basically no faith that this app will get better

Finally there's no way to book a set of desks for a team, seems like a common enough use case.

Ridiculous to make me go through the procedure of installing a completely fresh app for this. The poor quality of this app makes me less likely to go into the office on some days.

And then being taken back to the main screen (re-select desk instead of room) and go through 6 steps again. Also no indication of whether I already booked a desk that day.
